</site><head title="Extension Step| verifyContent"/><section title="Description"><b>Compares the current response with an expected file. Supports content filters such as <stepref name="lineSeparatorFilter" category=""/> and <stepref name="replaceFilter" category=""/> and the nested <stepref name="table" category="Core"/> step.</b></section><section title="Parameters"><attributes><attribute><name>description</name><description>The description of this test step.</description><required>no</required></attribute><attribute><name>mode</name><description>The diff mod to use for comparison. Possible values are "auto" (the default, uses "text" or "bin" depending on the type of the content to compare), "text" (performs a unified diff like diff), "bin" (compares byte per byte and displays differences in hex format), and "regexPerLine" (each line of the reference file is a regex that should match the actual content).</description><required>no</required></attribute><attribute><name>referenceFile</name><description>The file to compare to</description><required>yes</required></attribute><attribute><name>readFiltered</name><description>Indicates that when reading <em>referenceFile</em> that the content should be filtered.</description><required>no, default is
					true</required></attribute><attribute><name>htmlId</name><description>The id of an <key>HTML</key> element. If present, processing will be limited to this element. Will be ignored if a nested <stepref name="table" category=""/> step is used.</description><required>no</required></attribute><attribute><name>xpath</name><description>An XPath expression identifying an <key>HTML</key> element. If present, processing will be limited to this element. Will be ignored if <em>htmlId</em> is set or if a nested <stepref name="table" category=""/> step is used.</description><required>no</required></attribute></attributes></section><section title="Nested Parameters"><attributes><attribute><name>table</name><description>To locate a specific cell in a specific table on the page.</description><required>no</required></attribute><attribute><name>step</name><description>A webtest step.</description><required>yes</required></attribute></attributes></section><section title="Details"><post>

